":52023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T09:52:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>叫隻狗做姨丈</blockquote><br />\n笑到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5cc89d0bc70e918b6fba1805db153ca053e06d46","tid":96942,"uid":15206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T09:52:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你呀姨同彭健新個case有d似</blockquote><br />\n你呀姨同ok仔應該幾襯<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2160736dfe5bc9e8a9fefb727c089cd10fb14ac8","tid":96942,"uid":49359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T10:04:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我呀哥見我開左post有d補充<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n順年齡係<br />\n<br />\n姨媽<br />\n舅父<br />\n我媽<br />\n大姨<br />\njack姨<br />\n細舅父 <br />\n<br />\n咁呢, 大舅父就繼承父業, 做製衣, 已經發左達, 好多個十億身家, 長居大陸既, 就同我阿婆(佢阿媽) 反左面架啦, 返親去阿婆度佢都鬧既<br />\n<br />\n姨媽幫舅父打工, 搵萬幾一個月, 一星期做7 日, 日日做十幾個鐘。老公死左, 有個好細個開始領養既女(因為自己生唔到)<br />\n<br />\njack姨呢,屋企讀最多書, 好似有考會考, 當年做銀行, 有個男朋友, 拍左4-5 年拖好似傾緊結婚時被飛, 然後試過自殺, 但不成功。之後就專心養狗, 就係佢成日要我地同佢隻狗拜年先俾利是。佢地D 狗食靈芝食牛扒, 每個月伙食成萬蚊。<br />\n<br />\n大姨係我婆最錫又最嬲既女, 因為好大脾氣, 都係同我婆反左面既。佢同左一個以前喺我地製衣廠做野既細過佢既男仔結左婚, 個男人而家發左達, 所以佢基本上成世人都無做過野。兩個仔, 一個科大一個港大, 科大讀到差D 俾人QUIT, 無HON 畢業, 唔鍾意打工, 成日拎屋企錢去做生意, 但SO FAR 都未有成功過(同我好FRD 既但係, 細我兩年); 港大仔就成日呃呃氹氹, 靠關係走後門而家做緊IBANK , 屋企人就覺得佢好勁咁。翠姨份人好要威, 所以我同我妹讀書叻, 佢就好唔憤氣既,<br />\n<br />\n細舅父就有唐氏綜合症, 斷左一隻手既, 智力好似得5 歲左右</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咪講咁多，好易認</blockquote><br />\n你舅父都幾仆街幾十億身家萬幾蚊請自己家姐"},{"pid":"181f1482c955944a49e619f5f99ab1e9dda3b381","tid":96942,"uid":77867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T10:06:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>叫隻狗做姨丈</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n屌佢仲要唔係同隻狗一齊出現，通常係咁<br />\n<br />\n我: 新年快樂 青春常駐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n姨: 嗯，咁呀jack呢 (佢隻鳩狗) 唔同jack拜埋年唔比利是你架<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我：。。。。。<br />\n姨：（keep 住鳩笑）<br />\n我：噢妳話姨丈呀。。。"},{"pid":"14080ac9d4d0bab4a480c71e335cded38ad45310","tid":96942,"uid":11805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T10:13:31.000Z","msg":"我係你KongU表哥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7dc88fc66b843635c7f6d790fa0006ecf790d829","tid":96942,"uid":49387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T10:15:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我係你KongU表哥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28ddcecbd55834642eabe83d85cff2d6eabdabda","tid":96942,"uid":30051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T10:15:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8947209f804bb93412075aaca1ca753443c3478c","tid":96942,"uid":67432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T10:36:37.000Z","msg":"絲打唔驚自爆?"}]}